  "text": "The proposed approach aims to unify SCT and ICT into one global data association. The inputs are the observations and the outputs are final trajectories. The data association is modeled as a global maximum a posteriori (MAP) problem which shares the same MAP formulation with Zhang et al. [CITATION_1] . The difference is that the input in the proposed solution are tracklets instead of object detections. And the association aims to solve the wrong matching and tracklet missing problems in ICT, while Zhang et al. [CITATION_2] applies it on SCT. We outline the variable definitions in Tab. I.",
